Start  
    Set correct Num = a random number between 1 and 100  
    Declare userGuess  

    Do  
         "Enter your guess (1-100):"  
        Input userGuess  

        If the user Guess < correct number, then  
           "Too low. Try again."  
        Else If user Guess > correct Num Then  
            Display "Too high. Try again."  
        Else  
           "Correct! You guessed the number."  
        End If  
    While user Guess != correct Num
End
